NK010(tha)025:1: phan gnod las tshogs rdo rje pha lam bzhugs /
NK010(tha)025:2: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen khrag 'thung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)025:3: phan gnod kyi las tshogs gnyis las /
NK010(tha)025:6: sems dpa' chen pos phan pa'i le'u bshad du gsol /
NK010(tha)025:7: las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig /
NK010(tha)025:8: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sngags 'di byin gyis brlabs nas gsungs so //
NK010(tha)025:9: b+hur khung ma h+aa pra na tse b+hu rtse b+hi ma na se byi ta kro ti /
NK010(tha)025:10: shi ma go khu ling h+aum h+aum phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)025:11: b+hur khung ho ra re ni ho ya b+h+yo /
NK010(tha)025:12: rat+na kha hi b+hi ma na se mo /
NK010(tha)025:13: shing mo ku lu ku lu h+aum h+aum phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)025:14: b+hur khung ma h+aa pra na tse bi ma na se /
NK010(tha)025:15: u tsush+ma kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)025:16: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis snying po 'di gsungs nas mi snang bar gyur to //
NK010(tha)025:17: sems dpa' chen po rkyen bzlog pa'i rdzas gang lags /
NK010(tha)025:18: las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig /
NK010(tha)025:20: gal te gso bar 'dod na gu gul la sngags
NK010(tha)025:21: kyis btab ste bsregs nas brgya rtsa brgyad btab na
NK010(tha)025:24: sdigs mdzub kyi phyag rgya bstan na ser ba 'chad /
NK010(tha)025:27: rims nad na ba la bya mo nag mo'i dong rus chus btab bo //
NK010(tha)025:28: klu'i rten yod na thal ba gtsang ma la sngags
NK010(tha)025:29: btab na mi de la sems ngan med par 'gyur
NK010(tha)025:30: ro // mche ba can za ba yod na /
NK010(tha)025:31: kha nas zan la sngags btab la sbyin no //
NK010(tha)025:32: klad pa gzer na gang na ba la phur pa la sngags btab pa'am /
NK010(tha)025:33: yang na gur gum mam tsan+dana la sogs la bya'o //
NK010(tha)025:34: bal nad na ba la phab zer la basngagasa te khu ba btsir la blud do //
NK010(tha)025:35: mi lo nad kyis na ba la /
NK010(tha)025:36: nad pa'i ming shog bu la bris la /
NK010(tha)025:37: nad pa'i khri 'og tu bcug la sngags gdab bo //
NK010(tha)025:38: skrangs pa la nyin mtshan du gdab bo //
NK010(tha)025:39: pha rol smra shes par bya na /
NK010(tha)025:40: kho'i ming rus khar gzhug go //
NK010(tha)025:41: ra lug la spyang ki 'ong na /
NK010(tha)025:42: dom pho dom mo'i ske ru sngags bris pa gdags so //
NK010(tha)025:44: de rnams la gu gul bsregs shing bsgrub pa'o //
NK010(tha)025:45: ling tog la sngags 'di phus gdab bo //
NK010(tha)025:46: chu 'gag na gla ba dang mar la gdab /
NK010(tha)025:47: sbos nas na na chang khye'u'i chu la bsres nas gdab bo //
NK010(tha)025:48: de nyid la sngags de btang ngo //
NK010(tha)025:49: 'dre'i gnod pa che na chu dang yungs kar la basngagasa la blud do //
NK010(tha)025:50: nad pa srung bar byed na /
NK010(tha)025:51: sngags bar ma chad par bzlas na /
NK010(tha)025:53: sos ka dag gi dus su yungs kar la sngags btab na chang thub par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)025:54: des zho yang thub par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)025:56: sgros bsregs shing sngags bzlas so //
NK010(tha)025:57: ba lang khong log na nyung dkar la sngags bzlas so //
NK010(tha)025:58: zhing la srin za na nyung dkar dang che sra
NK010(tha)025:59: ste zhing mtha' bskor zhing btab na ngos gcig tu
NK010(tha)025:60: 'agro'o // so la srin za na bcas te thad kar gdab bo //
NK010(tha)025:61: mig la srin za na bud shing gdab bo //
NK010(tha)025:62: bang mdzod la gnod par byed na tsan+dana nam shug
NK010(tha)025:63: pa'i phur pa sor bcu gnyis pa la basngagasa la
NK010(tha)025:64: / thod pa mtshan ngan 'bru nag pos bkang la
NK010(tha)025:65: dar nag po'i cod pan dang bcas pas h+aum k+aa
NK010(tha)025:66: / ra'am / rnam par rgyal bar mnga' gsol la /
NK010(tha)025:71: de nas rdo rje 'dus pas 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK010(tha)025:72: dam chos gzhung spyod rnal 'byor la //
NK010(tha)025:73: bar chod sku dgra byung gyur na //
NK010(tha)025:74: gzhan nyid skrag par bya ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)025:75: thog dang ser ba dbab pa dang //
NK010(tha)025:76: mi nad phyugs nad btang ba dang //
NK010(tha)025:77: smyo ba dang ni 'bog pa dang //
NK010(tha)025:78: myos pa dang ni lkugs pa dang //
NK010(tha)025:79: 'thab tu gzhug dang skrod gyur na //
NK010(tha)025:80: thabs dang rim pa ji ltar lags //
NK010(tha)025:81: dpa' bo khyod kyis bshad du gsol //
NK010(tha)025:83: gsol ba'i don thugs su chud nas /
NK010(tha)025:84: gzhan skrag par byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NK010(tha)025:86: de la thogs dbab par 'dod pas /
NK010(tha)025:87: lcags sna lnga la drag po'i phur pa byas te /
NK010(tha)025:88: klu nag po'i gnas su dkyil 'khor nag po gru gsum byas la /
NK010(tha)025:89: 'bras kyi zan la klu rgyal gzugs byas la /
NK010(tha)025:90: klu yi rgyal po dgug gzhug bstim nas ni /
NK010(tha)025:91: phur pa rdo rje 'dus pa'i bsnyen pa 'bum byas te /
NK010(tha)025:92: klu'i rgyal po la btab ste /
NK010(tha)025:93: klu gnad la bor na thog dus su phebs par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)025:94: ser ba dbab par 'dod pas sher shing nag po la phur pa byas te /
NK010(tha)025:96: khyab 'jug gza' rgyal gzugs byas la /
NK010(tha)025:97: bdag nyid lha'i rnal 'byor gdengs dang ldan par byas la /
NK010(tha)025:98: lce bog nag po'i dud pas bdug cing /
NK010(tha)025:100: khyab 'jug nyid gzugs la phab ste /
NK010(tha)025:101: phur pas btab la gnad la phab na /
NK010(tha)025:102: ser ba dus bzhin du phebs par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)025:104: mi gang rims kyis shi ba'i mchog phur g.yas pa thogs la /
NK010(tha)025:105: dbang gi dkyil 'khor zla gam dmar po byas te /
NK010(tha)025:106: rims kyis shi ba'i ro ras la /
NK010(tha)025:107: bram ze nag mo'i mnga' khrag gis ming rus bris te /
NK010(tha)025:108: zi ra nag po'i dud pas bdug ste /
NK010(tha)025:110: pad+ma 'dus pa'i bsnyen pa 'bum byas te /
NK010(tha)025:111: phur pa btab ste dgra bo'i nyal sar sbas na /
NK010(tha)025:114: seng ldeng gi phur pa thogs te /
NK010(tha)025:115: phyugs nad kyis shi ba'i khrag gis ma he'am rta
NK010(tha)025:116: mchog gi pags pa la dgra bo'i phyugs nor gyi
NK010(tha)025:117: ming bris la phur pa btab ste /
NK010(tha)025:118: phyugs lhas sam bres su btab na /
NK010(tha)025:121: bram ze'i mchog phur g.yas pa thogs la /
NK010(tha)025:122: nags tshal chen po'i gnas su dkyil 'khor ser po gru bzhi gcig byas la /
NK010(tha)025:123: r+ts+wa dgun ma'i lo ma la gzugs byas la /
NK010(tha)025:124: d+ha du ra'i du bas bdug ste /
NK010(tha)025:125: rin chen 'dus pa'i bsnyeen pa 'bum byas la /
NK010(tha)025:127: phur pas lce la btab ste yi dwags gnas pa'i sar sbas na /
NK010(tha)025:130: g.yer shing ngam skyer pa'i phur pa thogs te /
NK010(tha)025:131: ras sam gro ga la a dkar gyi khu bas ming rus bris nas /
NK010(tha)025:132: gong ma bzhin du las byas te /
NK010(tha)025:133: 'byung po gnas pa'i sar sbas na mi de 'bog par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)025:135: rgyal rigs kyi mchog phur g.yas pa thogs te /
NK010(tha)025:136: ri bo 'dus pa'i rtser dkyil 'khor dkar po zlum po byas te /
NK010(tha)025:137: dug shing gdug pa'i lo ma la gzugs byas la /
NK010(tha)025:138: tsan+dana dkar po'i thang chus ming rus bris la /
NK010(tha)025:139: mi tshil gyi du bas bdug la /
NK010(tha)025:140: bud+d+ha 'dus pa'i bsnyen pa 'bum byas la gzugs la phab ste /
NK010(tha)025:141: spyi bo'i gtsug tu phur pa btab ste /
NK010(tha)025:142: ma mo'i gnas su sbas na /
NK010(tha)025:143: mi de shin tu yang myos par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)025:147: shog shog gam shing shun la sngar lkugs nas shi
NK010(tha)025:148: ba'i klad khrag gis ming rus bris te gong ma
NK010(tha)025:149: bzhin phur pa lce la btab nas /
NK010(tha)025:150: sa bdag gnas pa'i sar sbas na /
NK010(tha)025:151: mi de shin tu yang lkugs par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)025:153: dmangs rigs kyi mchog phur g.yas pa thogs la /
NK010(tha)025:154: shing rkang gcig gi gnas su dkyil 'khor nag po gru gsum byas te /
NK010(tha)025:155: 'ug pa'i pags pa la bya rog gi khrag gis kho dang mdza' ba'i ming bris te /
NK010(tha)025:156: sbrul dang rmigs bu lto sbyar ba'i bar du bkug ste /
NK010(tha)025:158: rdo sol nag po'i mes bsregs te /
NK010(tha)025:159: las rab 'dus pa'i bsnyen pa 'bum byas te /
NK010(tha)025:160: ming byang gnyis kyi mtshams su phur pa btab ste /
NK010(tha)025:161: dur khrod kyi shing rings la gtags te /
NK010(tha)025:162: rlung chen po la phyar na /
NK010(tha)025:165: smra shing gi phur pa thogs te /
NK010(tha)025:166: lung gi rnga mo'i pags pa la /
NK010(tha)025:167: rak+tasa ming rus yul khyim gyi ming bris la /
NK010(tha)025:168: gong ma bzhin du las byas te /
NK010(tha)025:169: khyim gyi rtsig rmang du sbas nas /
NK010(tha)025:170: mi de yul dbyung bar 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)025:171: gzhan yang bskrad pa'i las kyi rim pa 'di ni /
NK010(tha)025:172: las dang po pa rnams kyi spyod yul min no //
NK010(tha)025:173: ting nge 'dzin las su rung zhing rtags mthong zhing
NK010(tha)025:174: drod tshad zin pa rnams kyis ni gdon mi za
NK010(tha)025:178: dbye ba la sogs pa'i drag shul gyi las chen
NK010(tha)025:179: rnam pa tha dad pa'i las tshogs yod kyang da
NK010(tha)025:180: ni lnga brgya'i tha ma nyid kyi phyir na chos
NK010(tha)025:181: nyid byang chub sems kyi phur bu'i ngang du rnam
NK010(tha)025:182: par rig byed kyi las nyon bsad pa la brtson
NK010(tha)025:183: par byas pas ngan 'gro'i go 'phang las phyir phyogs
